description:
It was discovered that PHP incorrectly handled certain files.
An attacker could possibly use this issue to cause a denial of service.
title: PHP vulnerability
summary: php5, php7.0, php7.2, php7.3, php7.4 vulnerability
action: In general, a standard system update will make all the necessary changes.
isummary:
PHP could be made to crash if it received a specially crafted
file.
